  CD [Dn:]path ..

Low Memory, Internal

Sets the current working directory of
drive Dn: to the specified path.

Multiple parameters are not supported
by the internal version.

Examples:

CD D4:>TOOLS>SOURCES
Changes the path starting at the main
directory on drive D4.

CD TEXT
Changes the path to directory TEXT on
the current drive, starting from the
current directory.
